<br>
I noticed the number of Novice Docs tripled about a week after the &quot;pets for all&quot; patch.<br>
<br>
So I agree that no exp for healing your own pet is fair.  Medics don't get exp from healing themselves either.  <br>
<br>
But, hopefully they are looking at unnerfing this nerf a little.  There was a dev post on this saying they might allow partial exp for healing of others pets.<br>
<br>
It doesn't fix the game mechanic tho for CHs or real non-exploiting Docs.  Now the penalty for using a pet as a tank is lower exp for the Doc even after they unnerf and give partial exp.  That stings.<br>
